Package org.eng.aisp.feature.processor.vector

Provides implementations of feature processors over vectors of double values.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSingletonFeatureExtractor
    Extends the super class enable implementations that collapse the matrix of feature data into a single feature.
    AbstractVectorMappingFeatureProcessor
    Extends the super class to map an array of feature data to a new array feature data.
    DeltaFeatureProcessor
    Computes the delta (defined as the standard way in speech processing) of features with options to normalize and scale features.
    L1MagnitudeFeatureProcessor  
    LpMagnitudeFeatureProcessor
    Extend the super class to use LpDistanceFunction.
    MagnitudeFeatureProcessor
    Uses a distance metric to compute the magnitude of the features.
    NormalizingFeatureProcessor
    Enables the normalization and mean removal of features.
    PipelinedFeatureProcessor
    Allows sequential/pipelined execution of IFeatureProcessor instances.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DeltaFeatureProcessor.ScaleMethod
